Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.05,0:00:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,400)\fad(1000,000)}圣天空战记
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是只要坠入爱河每个人都会变得如此孤单?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是正拥抱着比黑暗要更深沉的苦楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切必定都是为了让我俩能绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直用心凝视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是在寒冷的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在用泪水来呼唤你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你早就给了我 最宝贵的坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 愛したら誰もが こんな孤独になるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 暗闇よりも深い苦しみ 抱きしめてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもが二人 輝くためきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心で見つめている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒い夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙で今呼びかける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束などいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君がくれた大切な強さだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.40,0:01:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.40,0:01:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.24,0:01:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个先待在那里待命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.80,0:01:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.97,0:01:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻之谷并无入□
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.81,0:01:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其入□是不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.65,0:02:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界的尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.86,0:02:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舵…舵无法控制
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.66,0:02:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮力计破表了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.64,0:02:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.97,0:02:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻之谷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.77,0:02:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.11,0:02:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚特兰提斯的遭到遗忘之都城
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.49,0:02:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是幻之谷?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.93,0:02:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.20,0:02:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.64,0:02:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:02:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.77,0:02:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.97,0:03:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.51,0:03:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.61,0:03:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳在下面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.21,0:03:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里究竟是个什么样的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.19,0:03:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我见过这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我在梵濒临死亡时所预见到的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.74,0:03:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.55,0:03:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尼利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.56,0:03:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.60,0:03:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母后?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.91,0:04:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.05,0:04:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以过去,谢蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.30,0:04:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.94,0:04:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.47,0:04:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.97,0:04:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚特兰提斯文字的石碑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.01,0:04:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.85,0:04:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是亚特兰提斯的遗迹\N幻之谷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.38,0:04:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道上面写着什么吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.75,0:04:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新星运记,十三之月
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.82,0:04:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看得懂吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.31,0:05:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等亚特兰提斯末裔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.94,0:05:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被称为龙神人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生于位在幻之月的亚特兰提斯之都
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.35,0:05:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻…幻之月?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.39,0:05:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚特兰提斯是幻之月之民?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.79,0:05:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚特兰提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.86,0:05:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其力量强大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并自封为超越神明之存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.33,0:05:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创造出不祥之机械
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此机械可将人的意念转化为力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.77,0:05:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所不知,无所不能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.21,0:05:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至让自己背上生出羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变了自身的容貌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.18,0:05:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个坠子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.38,0:06:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥远的意念让天空中出现一颗新星"盖亚"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.82,0:06:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此乃亚特兰提斯之意念
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.26,0:06:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"愚昧我等所造就出的过往不会再重复"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.20,0:06:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包含着此一令人伤感之愿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.57,0:06:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盖亚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.20,0:06:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是颗为天拥抱,为水所爱,为大地所滋养的美丽星球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.34,0:06:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盖亚是由意念之力所创?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能将意念转化成力量的机械?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.72,0:07:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是所谓的亚特兰提斯之谜吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这个会…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.22,0:07:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我交给她的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.46,0:07:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.76,0:07:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.97,0:07:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来那是前世的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.77,0:07:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.11,0:07:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是龙神人染满鲜血的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流于梵大人体内之血的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.08,0:07:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尔卡斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.09,0:07:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.92,0:07:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您必须正视自己的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.43,0:07:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神人为亚特兰提斯的末裔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.50,0:07:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不使盖亚步上亚特兰提斯的后尘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.94,0:07:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您注定要与其相抗衡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.94,0:08:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您得与艾斯嘉科尼一同战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.78,0:08:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.78,0:08:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不想再战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.29,0:08:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵跟亚连他们都在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟看到了什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我会…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.14,0:08:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连,你来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.75,0:08:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我的愿望终于实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.29,0:08:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…该从什么开始说好呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.09,0:08:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今,还有什么好说的?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你当上天空骑士了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.53,0:08:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你母亲她一定很开心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.33,0:09:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你母亲…安希亚过得好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.67,0:09:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.24,0:09:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在你外出旅行的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.38,0:09:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.31,0:09:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安希亚她…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.98,0:09:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要哭?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.62,0:09:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.75,0:09:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要痛失所爱之人都会流泪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.56,0:09:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本就不爱她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.09,0:09:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对,一直,憎恨着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.87,0:09:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.70,0:09:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.28,0:09:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下来!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.99,0:09:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.62,0:09:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.46,0:10:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕,状况似乎不太稳定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去我们恐怕很难离开这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.17,0:10:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里虽然是盖亚却也不是盖亚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.14,0:10:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本无计可施
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.44,0:10:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,你没有办法吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.45,0:10:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请引导梵,亚连还有我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.78,0:10:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.65,0:10:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以使用意念之力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.79,0:10:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意念源自于不安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那股意念会让不安成为现实
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.87,0:10:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的意念…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.34,0:10:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.68,0:10:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在折磨梵他们的其实就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:10:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.99,0:10:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.39,0:11:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.79,0:11:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为自己占卜到的是未来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.19,0:11:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其实不然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.77,0:11:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我害的?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.47,0:11:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那不安的内心藉由占卜憎强
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在数种未来当中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.88,0:11:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选择了悲伤的结局
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.12,0:11:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对,你的心目前仍充满了不安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.00,0:11:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的错吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.13,0:11:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我将不幸的未来吸引过来的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.67,0:11:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是因为我的意念…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.08,0:11:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.35,0:12:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.68,0:12:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.29,0:12:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要相信他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.99,0:12:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信你喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.43,0:12:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外婆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.70,0:12:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈兵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.09,0:12:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们正在追杀从幻之谷出来的我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.29,0:12:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了要知道亚特兰提斯之谜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.30,0:12:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚特兰提斯?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.98,0:13:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多伦卡喀大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.65,0:13:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经拿到那样东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.93,0:13:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我费了那么多工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.86,0:13:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混帐…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.03,0:13:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使失去家庭,丢掉性命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.64,0:13:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是不肯将幻之谷的秘密告诉我是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.58,0:13:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚特兰提斯之力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.19,0:13:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意念的力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.49,0:13:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再让我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.83,0:13:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再让我见那名少女一面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.41,0:14:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.37,0:14:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会还保持着那时候的模样呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.52,0:14:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.45,0:14:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的亚特兰提斯之谜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的意念之力,原来是那么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.56,0:14:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那个时候果然没想错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.83,0:14:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…给你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能带着这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.37,0:14:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思念会成真
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.64,0:14:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便相隔遥远也能穿越时间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.75,0:14:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跨越时空
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.10,0:15:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉,安希亚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.23,0:15:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷恩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.93,0:15:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲她…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.00,0:15:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她到死都还爱着父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.64,0:15:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而父亲您其实也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.01,0:15:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直爱着她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你又为什么要…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.71,0:15:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为了家庭而结婚生子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.98,0:15:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾打算压抑自己,就这么过一辈子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.08,0:16:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但人就是会有股想要逃离既有命运的冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.26,0:16:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次见到那名少女时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.16,0:16:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.13,0:16:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都爱着安希亚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有你,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.44,0:16:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人真是愚昧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么亚特兰提斯之力,什么意念
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.68,0:16:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却连自己的想法都没弄懂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安希亚
