Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.55,0:17:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总觉得不太妙
